OL,3,CMan charged with murder after 43-year-
OL,4,Cold died in south Bristol home
OL,6,FA man has appeared in court charged
OL,7,Fwith the murder of James Bruce in
OL,8,FBristol last year.
OL,10,FThe 43-year-old died at his home in
OL,11,FCoronation Road, Southville, on 2
OL,12,FMarch last year.
OL,14,FPiers Hansen, 42, from Brislington,
OL,15,Fwas originally charged with
OL,16,Fmanslaughter, however during a hearing
OL,17,Fat Bristol Crown Court it was
OL,18,Fconfirmed he will now face a murder
OL,19,Fcharge in connection with Mr Bruce's
OL,20,Fdeath.
