OL,6,FHansen has not yet submitted a plea
OL,7,Fand has been remanded until 6
OL,8,FSeptember, with a provisional trial
OL,9,Fdate set for 2 December.
OL,11,FMr Bruce's family have told about the
OL,12,Fchange and are continuing to receive
OL,13,Fsupport from family liaison officers
OL,14,Ffrom Avon and Somerset Police.
